			<p class="first_paragraph">
				As you watch the film this week, try to think about these questions: What holds this film together? If you don’t find a cause-and-effect relationship between individual scenes, can you find other types of connections? Similar ideas or themes? What types of things are repeated throughout the film, and how might they provide for some sort of unity?
			</p>
